    <h1>Contact</h1>
    <p></p>
    <p>Reaching out is easy! Catch me on <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/davidpattenaude">LinkedIn</a> or email me at <a href="mailto:david@pattenau.de">david@pattenau.de</a>.</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>